&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.insightsbot.com/blog/McTKK/python-one-hot-encoding-with-scikit-learn"&gt;Insightsbot - Python One Hot Encoding with SciKit Learn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
